					<div class="avatar"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/bc96451301455d6eef7c14d57fb50ed4?s=30&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-30 photo' height='30' width='30' /></div>					<cite class="fn">Esther</cite>				</div>
